    "description": "Peace is Your Destiny is a relaxing trip across an everlasting and colorful ocean. Clear islands by rolling your cube to match colored tiles. You will uncover surprises along the way towards a calmer and <strong>chill mindset</strong>. Created for players to enjoy calming puzzles and retreat into a<strong> beautiful minimalist world</strong>.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373080/extras/8571798e8f77e953d5d2a454821f4034.poster.avif?t=1681533815\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373080/extras/8571798e8f77e953d5d2a454821f4034.webm?t=1681533815\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373080/extras/8571798e8f77e953d5d2a454821f4034.mp4?t=1681533815\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Specially Designed for the People who Suffering from <strong>Anxiety or Stress</strong></li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373080/extras/956f5af16b9b124f9a8484a5bcab991d.poster.avif?t=1681533815\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373080/extras/956f5af16b9b124f9a8484a5bcab991d.webm?t=1681533815\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373080/extras/956f5af16b9b124f9a8484a5bcab991d.mp4?t=1681533815\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Simple tile matching gameplay that is easy to learn but<strong> hard to master</strong>.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373080/extras/75d7294b6e101275046acfe5e97aec3d.poster.avif?t=1681533815\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373080/extras/75d7294b6e101275046acfe5e97aec3d.webm?t=1681533815\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373080/extras/75d7294b6e101275046acfe5e97aec3d.mp4?t=1681533815\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Endless islands to complete -<strong> built to generate millions of unique layouts and color combinations</strong>.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373080/extras/ace9da3d2aa3906c200e5d1a87aa4a1b.poster.avif?t=1681533815\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373080/extras/ace9da3d2aa3906c200e5d1a87aa4a1b.webm?t=1681533815\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373080/extras/ace9da3d2aa3906c200e5d1a87aa4a1b.mp4?t=1681533815\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Colorful<strong> minimalist visuals</strong> that constantly change as you play.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373080/extras/663458b5806481948dbf470e0033a542.poster.avif?t=1681533815\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373080/extras/663458b5806481948dbf470e0033a542.webm?t=1681533815\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373080/extras/663458b5806481948dbf470e0033a542.mp4?t=1681533815\" type=\"video/mp4\